---
description: Keep documentation in sync
globs: ["src/**", "docs/**"]
---

After making changes to the codebase:
1. Update docs/FEATURES.md if features were added, changed, or removed
2. Update docs/CODE_REVIEW.md if bugs were fixed or new issues found
3. Update docs/DEFERRED.md if items were deferred or completed
4. Update docs/ARCHITECTURE.md if the tech stack or data flow changed
5. Update docs/IDEAS.md if new ideas or reminders came up

All docs in docs/ are living documents that must stay in sync with the code.
